{"tid":1476461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港人同我入哂黎] 大家一齊講返6月9號到而家發生過咩事，一齊整個網記低呢場「革命」！！","createTime":"2019-08-15T22:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T23:07:28.000Z","uid":232014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a3454915671a3de349e1509574832be23a98ba5","tid":1476461,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T22:36:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我發現香港人實在係太善忘，又或者係因為每日發生既突發事實在太多，成日都唔記得哂之前發生過啲咩重大事件。就好似葉虎架車，咁重要既事而家已經一字不提。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以而家我想大家一齊講返每一件事出黎，然後有冇人識整網站可以將每一件事都放入一個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>屬於香港人既網</strong></span></span>，等香港人得閒就攞出黎回顧下，再<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">掀返起大家616既果團火！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">暫時我有9個大主題：</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n「革命」因由：</span></span>林鄭係都要送中<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">市民抗爭手法：</span></span>遊行，衝立法會，罷工，塞機場塞鐵，前線勇武，圍警總，816撳錢...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警察濫暴/捕：</span></span>大把，有排搵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作：721元朗，仲有北角，荃灣？<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">政府既無能：</span></span>林鄭同盧偉聰錄音機，李家超立會同記者會既錄音機，仲有建制既謬論，何君堯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聯署同聲明：</span></span>好多，好似有人整合哂？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">外國既聲援：</span></span>英國美國加拿大法國澳洲啲相攞哂出黎，仲有攬炒巴既standwithhk<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">藍絲們既謬論：</span></span>Facebook，其他媒體相信大家都backup左唔少<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">社評：</span></span>社會有地位既聲音，例如何韻詩係聯合國既發言<br />\n<br />\n每一個主題都好多好多材料，我自己真係搵唔哂咁多，畢竟2個月個個禮拜都有野爆出黎，所以真係要靠咁多位喇！！<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩主題要加？我諗緊「義士重大事件」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港重大事件回顧tg:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/letsnotforgethk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fletsnotforgethk&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=66dc61a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/letsnotforgethk</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家發揮下你地既記憶，一齊記低佢！"},{"pid":"7e7b5c0d53e68d14177a99a7d42dc25d1e0d09a9","tid":1476461,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T22:37:30.000Z","msg":"6月9號<br />\n<br />\n百萬人遊行<br />\n夜晚第一次圍立會<br />\n第一次被清場"},{"pid":"504a33367217c183e38b58dcdeb345c705ea5a9a","tid":1476461,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T22:38:56.000Z","msg":"612<br />\n<br />\n三罷<br />\n中信<br />\n有個義士企係到就比幾個速龍推地下 禁住黎打"},{"pid":"c92df492a6eb440edf4f00e9a1c6465e2f6a4b84","tid":1476461,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T22:39:38.000Z","msg":"616 <br />\n<br />\n二百萬人遊行<br />\n梁義士 太古廣場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0d262326f8150e182587018836a929524df506","tid":1476461,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T22:41:06.000Z","msg":"612 <br />\n<br />\n比人射中彈 噴血果個義士<br />\n外國佬坐街邊照比人胡椒噴霧"},{"pid":"fe148f4d2c7e5b0140aa1447eedafb3bf6e87382","tid":1476461,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T22:41:31.000Z","msg":"一齊創建更多歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bfa3df0f32f29926836611950defce843f20e9","tid":1476461,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T22:41:43.000Z","msg":"612 <br />\n<br />\n全民罷工<br />\n交通道路有「交通意外」"},{"pid":"e26262dd97502f665c1d037e355b5251f85cb1e3","tid":1476461,"uid":